  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她把豆子扔了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听着！”妈妈转向杰克，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别再说那些没用的豆子了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在回去睡觉！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚上不许吃饭！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克低下了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，妈妈。”他低声说，“对不起……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克慢慢地爬上台阶，来到阁楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈说得对。”杰克心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真傻，竟然会相信有魔法！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在我们没有钱，没有牛奶，也没有奶牛了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克爬上床，望向窗外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112435</EndMilliseconds>
