  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要一个大计划。”杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他有了一个主意！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明天我要去找那位奇怪的爷爷。”他心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要让他把米可还给我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，杰克一大早就起床了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170014</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看阁楼四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177177</EndMilliseconds>
